data.title: Your Hit Parade, 1943-1948,1982-08-05
data.text: This audio reel contains programs: It's Been A Long, Long Time - Dick Todd, Joan Edwards; 12/1/1945; To Each His Own - Andy Russell, Peggy Mann 10/5/1946; For Sentimental Reasons - Andy Russell, Dinah Shore 1/25/1947; Symphony - Dick Todd, Joan Edwards 1/11/1946; A Tree In The Meadow - Frank Sinatra, Eileen Wilson 9/11/1948; Nature Boy - Frank Sinatra, Beryl Davis; You'll Never Know; Frank Sinatra, Bea Wain 8/28/1943; I'll Be Seeing You - Frank Sinatra, Bea Wain 7/22/1944.
